{"tid":918480,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(走佬？）賀建奎「失蹤」 美教授疑參與研究遭大學調查","createTime":"2018-11-27T09:01:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-27T12:12:17.000Z","uid":36494,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1fb9175f598bf00bddc28c4277ae8e1ba047aba6","tid":918480,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T09:01:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181127&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=58962962\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181127%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D58962962&d=LFry4mU5MBWBgVoBxpk3xdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=fef59d39\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181127%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D58962962&h=ce0b4244\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181127&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=58962962</a> <br />\n【基因編輯嬰兒】賀建奎「失蹤」 美教授疑參與研究遭大學調查<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n深圳南方科技大學副教授、瀚海基因董事長賀建奎，昨日宣稱成功創造出世界首對基因編輯、對愛滋病具有免疫力的雙胞胎後，如同在全球科學界投擲了一顆重磅炸彈。賀建奎的老師、美國萊斯大學（Rice University）教授Michael Deem，傳聞也參與相關研究。萊斯大學今日凌晨對內地媒體指，相關研究違反科學倫理，已經對Deem展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">賀今日原定出席本港第二屆人類基因組編輯國際峯會開幕禮，但最終他沒有現身。明日亦有他主持的講座，但暫未有消息指他會否出席，去向成謎</span>。"},{"pid":"0a7a4e87ec3e65c45186d585676504d6d967ed1a","tid":918480,"uid":76705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T09:05:29.000Z","msg":"被失蹤<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbd4294040131c8bb6c70749b1369ba922027d53","tid":918480,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T09:08:12.000Z","msg":"玩大左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1e12017863542824ec5b4bf52dfdcce48d424be","tid":918480,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T09:10:21.000Z","msg":"賀生已變成...<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.kknews.cc/SIG=klc5pf/288s0004r08850s05o0p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-